{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b857d87f96","title":"对《中央音乐学院的意见》的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"649907abcb","index":0,"year":1964,"month":9,"day":27,"articleId":"b857d87f96"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd91dd8563","type":"paragraph","text":"布马扎：非常高兴有这个机会同您讨论问题。这是我们期待很久的日子。主席：很希望看到你们，我感到你们有个特点，你们比我们年青。你们是刚升起来的太阳。布马扎：但我们觉得毛主席永远年青，思想总是明智开朗，看问题很清楚。你的我们都详","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"a11246c13f","type":"paragraph","text":"细记录了下来，同去要汇报，要向党的干部传达。这次谈很有教育意义。谁知道可","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"cc1786688c","type":"paragraph","text":"能有一天在阿尔及利亚或非洲看到您。主席：我也希望。布思扎：二十年前亚洲人、并洲人都受人欺悔，过去亚洲人、非洲人都被岐视。如对中国和","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"b6013d0945","type":"paragraph","text":"日本不同对待，非洲人也如此。他们也想分化我们，说有一部分是好的，另一部分是","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"10a22e209e","type":"paragraph","text":"坏的。但现在我们自由了。主席：你们解放了。亚洲问题还大，美军基地在日本、南朝鲜、菲律宾、南越、泰国，在太","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"4de9057c19","type":"paragraph","text":"平洋西岸包围我们，威胁着我们，也威协着当地人民，也威协着印度尼西亚和锡兰。帝国主义受伤了，但是还没有死，要多少年，恐怕要一百年吧！那是下一辈子的事，但是我相信帝国主义总有一天要死亡的。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"a1b2ba51c4","type":"paragraph","text":"对《中央音乐学院的意见》的批示","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"8a61318f5c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年九月二十七日）××同志","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"cb78fe1a4e","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请一开。信是写得好的，问题是应该解决的，应朵取征求群众意见的方法，在教师、学生中先行讨论，收集意见。古为今用，洋为中用。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"739a0ee59f","type":"paragraph","text":"此信表示一派人的意见，可能有许多人不赞成","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"e834440406","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"5702c3178f","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十七日观看革命现代芭雷舞剧《冠色娘子军》后","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"164fe0c9bd","type":"paragraph","text":"的指示","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"b0b5e4231a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年十月八日）《红色娘子军》方向是对的，革命是成功的，艺术上也是好的。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"0df59ea276","type":"paragraph","text":"接见西南非妇女代表团的酸盐（摘象）","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"5c6e095e53","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年十月）","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"45a39e85e8","type":"paragraph","text":"要请你们给我们的青年人讲讲课，使他们不要忘记世界上受帝国主义、地主、资本家刻制、压道的人民。","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"},{"id":"7310bed76d","type":"paragraph","text":"61863","index":17,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96"}],"page":{"id":"552c85f844","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b857d87f96","start":199,"end":199}}}},"__N_SSG":true}